Instrument(s)/Platform(s): ELITech Clinical Systems Selectra Pro Series Analyzers
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for ELITech Clinical Systems ELICAL 2 calibrator and ELITROL I/II control sera for use on Selectra Pro Series Analyzers in clinical chemistry calibration and quality control.
Indications for Use Summary: ELICAL 2 is a multi-parametric calibrator for in vitro diagnostic use in calibration of ELITech Clinical Systems methods on Selectra Pro Series Analyzers; ELITROL I and II are control sera for in vitro diagnostic use in quality control of quantitative ELITech Clinical Systems methods on Selectra Pro Series Analyzers.
